#
# Purpose: Keep local-only workspace, editor, build, and scratch artifacts out of commits.
# Caller: Git status, add, and review workflows for this repository.
# Dependencies: Git ignore pattern matching and repository-local scratch conventions.
# Main Functions: Ignore generated outputs, local settings, logs, and planning scratch files.
# Side Effects: Hides matching untracked local files from normal Git status and add flows.
#
# Local workspace settings
.claude-skills/*
# Ignore everything inside .claude/ by default, then track plugin-shipped
# subagents and hook config. (settings.local.json and similar stay local.)
/.claude/*
!/.claude/agents/
!/.claude/hooks.json

# Editor folders
.idea/
.vscode/

# Native build artifacts
bin/
dist/
coverage.out
*.test
/claude-skills-bin
/claude-skills-bin.exe

# Rust build artifacts
/target/
# Cargo.lock is committed for reproducible binary builds per Cargo convention.

# Local assistant settings
.*/settings.local.json

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temp, patch, and log files
/.claude_tmp*
/.gh-*.log
*.log
*.tmp
*-cover.out
/$cover
*.bak
*.swp
*.orig
*.rej

# Local planning scratch files
plan.md
todo.md
todo.local.md

# Local validation and flow artifacts
VALIDATION_REPORT.md
flow-check.json
